# Verify-pipeline synthesized SwiftPM workdirs (build artifacts; index.json
# stays tracked). Matches any `.swiftinfer/verify-workdir/` — the fixture's
# and any incidental one at the repo root from a dev `swift-infer verify` run.
**/.swiftinfer/verify-workdir/

# Calibration triage decision files — regenerable per-cycle scratch produced
# by `discover-interaction --interactive` / the cycle re-triage. The durable
# record is the cycle-N findings doc worksheet + calibration-cycle-N-data/.
**/.swiftinfer/interaction-decisions.json
